Orienting Data

2414 subjects sequenced at 665027 locations used as input. Synchronized data to GRCh38/hg38 reference genome. Using Lift-over. 581 variants due to insfufficient mapping ifnormation 7 variants removed due to non SNP mutation (such as insertion and deletion).
